The Civilization possesses the supreme authority to:

1. Amend this Constitution through defined processes
2. Create new governing institutions
3. Dissolve existing institutions
4. Create new layers of governance
5. Restructure its organizational framework
6. Redistribute authority and power
7. Reinterpret the Constitution
8. Create new civilizations
9. Federate with other civilizations

Section 3.04: Constitutional Amendment Process

The Constitution may be amended through a process requiring:

1. Proposal by an authorized entity
2. Review by the Executive Council
